## 3. ⚠️ Improvements

| Area | Suggestion |
|------|-----------|
| **Timezone** | Store user's timezone in DB (`User.timezone`). Use `date-fns-tz` on the backend to convert slot times before returning |
| **Booking Confirmation** | Send a real confirmation email (nodemailer / Resend) instead of the fake "A calendar invitation has been sent…" message |
| **Slug Validation** | Add regex validation on backend: only allow `[a-z0-9-]`; the frontend modal has a hint but no enforcement |
| **Loading States** | Add skeleton loaders to [MeetingsPage](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/pages/MeetingsPage.tsx#6-113) and [AvailabilityPage](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/pages/AvailabilityPage.tsx#33-227) (only Dashboard shows `eventTypesLoading`) |
| **Pagination** | Add limit/offset to [getUpcoming](file:///e:/SCALER/BACKEND/src/controllers/booking.controller.js#36-52) / [getPast](file:///e:/SCALER/BACKEND/src/controllers/booking.controller.js#53-70) — no pagination means all bookings load in one request |
| **Input sanitization** | `name` and `email` in booking form: add trim + basic email regex validation on both frontend and backend |
| **Error handling** | Replace all `alert()` calls ([AvailabilityPage.tsx](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/pages/AvailabilityPage.tsx) L87, [BookingPage.tsx](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/pages/BookingPage.tsx) L134) with toast notifications |
| **Public booking auth** | `POST /api/booking` should be rate-limited (e.g. express-rate-limit) to prevent spam bookings |
| **DB indexes** | Add composite index on [Booking(date, eventTypeId, status)](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/pages/BookingPage.tsx#18-249) for the double-booking check query performance |
| **`description` field** | [EventType](file:///e:/SCALER/FRONTEND/src/app/context/AppContext.tsx#6-13) model has no `description` column — the frontend sends/stores it, but it's never persisted. Either add the column or remove the field from the form |

